<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海巫婆仔细地看了看小美人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要为你准备一个魔法药。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它能把你的尾巴变成腿和脚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”小美人鱼开心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有了腿，我就能走到陆地上，走近我的王子了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那么，他就一定会爱上我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得警告你。”海巫婆接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每当你站着的时候，都会很痛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在别人看来，你走起路来很优美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，你每走一步，都会像一个锋利的刀割你的脚一样痛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海巫婆停下来抚摸她的青蛙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她问小美人鱼：“你愿意为你所愿而受苦吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我当然愿意！”小美人鱼兴奋地回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为了活在地上世界并得到灵魂，我愿意做任何事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要记住，”海巫婆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一旦你变成了人，你就永远不可能再变回人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你永远不能再住在你父亲的王宫里或者和你的姐姐们玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不能再问奶奶问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不能再回到海底王国。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明白。”小美人鱼轻轻地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海巫婆盯着小美人鱼的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一件事，宝贝。”她接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果王子跟别人结婚，你就不能得到灵魂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他跟别人结婚的第二天早上，你就会死掉变成大海泡沫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我愿意冒险。”小美人鱼说，脸色变得苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道我要让王子爱上我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，孩子，为了确定我们的交易，你必须得付出代价。”海巫婆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你拥有所有人鱼中最美的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都说你的声音很特别。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你把你的声音给我，我就给你药。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，那我怎么告诉王子我爱他呢？”小美人鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么，你现在失去勇气了吗？”海巫婆笑着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”小美人鱼回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想起自己为家人们唱歌的时候。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想起那些幸福的时刻，小美人鱼觉得很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她慢慢地说：“我要把我的声音给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那跟我来吧。”海巫婆带着小美人鱼走进了她的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一进到里面，海巫婆就把一口大锅放到了地上冒着烟的坑上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海巫婆切了几条蛇和几只水母，把它们扔进了大锅，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还扔进去别的一些黏糊糊的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，海巫婆开始念咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小美人鱼请求，爱一个只活在地上世界的王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，她已经下了决心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她将拥有腿，我将拥有她的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>液体开始沸腾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鬼脸一样的烟雾从大锅里升起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法药做好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海巫婆把它倒进了一个小瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是你要的。”海巫婆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把瓶子递给小美人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼想说点什么，可是她发不出声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她美丽的声音消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在日出之前，游到海边上去。”海巫婆命令说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等你到了干的陆地，把药喝了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的尾巴就会变成一双腿脚。现在，去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼默默地点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>